data.value: Bloodbath Soul is a combination of Attack Up (L) and Evasion +2. It provides +20 Attack and +0.2 seconds of additional invincibility when dodging.\n\nTrue Bloodbath Soul additionally provides Composed, which grants a +10% charge rate for all Hunter Art, Valor, and Alchemy Gauges.

data.name: treeNode170.Tag
data.value:
When in Green, you get +10% raw. In Yellow, +15%. In Orange or Red Sharpness, you get +20%. 

 Originally in Gen, the values did not scale and were instead flat bonuses. Green granted +10 raw, Yellow +15, and Red/Orange +20. 

 Warning, dipping into Yellow and below causes the Low Sharpness Modifier to kick in, reducing your damage by up to 40%. Please see the associated entry in the glossary for more details on the LSM.

data.name: label87.Text
data.value: Weapons with innate Status damage will only apply their status a third of the time. This includes all Blademaster weapons and Bows. Bowguns that use Status-type shots and Bows that use Status Coatings apply them 100% of the time. KO and Exhaust will also always be applied, unless it's an SA Exhaust Phial, in which case, it follows the 33% rule. Uniquely, Bow Status Coatings deals different amount of status depending on the shot type.
